    <item>
      <title>供应担忧加剧，可可价格回升至每吨 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/cocoa-surges-back-to-10-000-a-ton-on-growing-supply-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球供应已经紧张，人们对西非产量下降的担忧加剧，可可期货价格攀升至近六个月来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/cocoa-surges-back-to-10-000-a-ton-on-growing-supply-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:30:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基汇资本牵头集团将为收购香港中心大厦的贷款进行再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/gaw-capital-led-group-to-refinance-loan-used-to-buy-hk-tower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由香港基金管理公司基汇资本牵头的投资财团正在寻求一笔 54 亿港元（6.94 亿美元）的贷款，以再融资用于收购太古城中心一期办公大楼的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/gaw-capital-led-group-to-refinance-loan-used-to-buy-hk-tower</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:23:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行行长 Dhingra 表示她支持“渐进式”降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/boe-s-dhingra-says-she-s-in-favor-of-gradual-rate-cuts-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行利率制定者斯瓦蒂·丁格拉警告称，高利率会抑制消费者支出和商业投资，从而对经济造成压力。在接受彭博社记者丽兹·伯登采访时，丁格拉表示，她支持“逐步”降低利率，长期中性利率可能在 2.5% 至 3.5% 之间。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/boe-s-dhingra-says-she-s-in-favor-of-gradual-rate-cuts-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:14:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
