      <title>华尔街债券卖家期待 2024 年获得更大奖金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/wall-street-s-bond-sellers-look-toward-bigger-2024-bonus-rewards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[招聘和薪酬专家表示，帮助公司出售债务的华尔街银行家将在 2024 年获得更大的奖金，如果发行趋势继续下去，明年可能会获得更高的奖励。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/wall-street-s-bond-sellers-look-toward-bigger-2024-bonus-rewards</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非橄榄球联盟阻止 Ackerley 私募股权收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/south-african-rugby-unions-block-ackerley-private-equity-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在竞争对手的提议公开后不久，南非橄榄球联盟的成员们拒绝了阿克利体育集团有限责任公司 (Ackerley Sports Group LLC) 对世界排名最高的国家橄榄球队的商业权利的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/south-african-rugby-unions-block-ackerley-private-equity-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 10:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
